      <li>An estimated 40-60 former POGO operators that migrated from the Philippines must comply within 180 days or face criminal penalties up to 10 years imprisonment and $250K fines.</li>
      <li>The framework includes FATF-aligned AML requirements including CDD, STR filing, 7-year record retention, and mandatory compliance officers.</li>
      <li>Cambodia's approach contrasts with Myanmar's regulatory vacuum and the UAE's premium resort-integrated model, positioning Cambodia as the structured middle path for offshore gaming regulation.</li>
